8","text":"2. Vías de Activación","guid":"42AR-SmcYCLx7s4Ar_qyeA","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"• Vía Clásica: Activada por complejos Ag-Ac.","guid":"BRPWAmCmZZ36LV6kOgcjWw","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"• C1 → C4 → C2 → C3 → C5.","guid":"we5ZrbHU10VTkQevOOFmQg","children":[]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"243","text":"• Vía Alternativa: Activada por superficies microbianas.","guid":"AoGmANxfYvGP-OVFqutlUA","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"• C3 espontáneo → Factor B → Factor D → C3 convertasa.","guid":"ph6DEQToiu-pjGvEPo3tog","children":[]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"243","text":"• Vía de las Lectinas: Activada por lectinas de unión a manosa.","guid":"Psph4rQWf1zeg2WZnFKEOQ","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"• MBL → MASP-1 y MASP-2 → C4 → C2 → C3 → C5.","guid":"6m-O9B9UXz86S1csiC7F9g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"238","text":"3. Formación del Complejo de\\NAtaque a la Membrana (MAC)","guid":"2VjC3C4jH69U7BcOicVk-A","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"• C5b se une a C6, C7, C8, y C9 formando un poro\\Nen la membrana del patógeno → Lisis celular.","guid":"4P5CkHw-WNKhXKrRLGyrEA","children":[]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"238","text":"4. Deficiencias del\\NComplemento","guid":"PSGB780YU1JIJLwH6Kr9bg","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"• Deficiencias en C1, C2, C4 → Enfermedades autoinmunes, infecciones bacterianas.","guid":"ItwnXJ0dBiajaYeYK1KDdg","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"252","text":"• Deficiencias en C3 → Infecciones bacterianas severas.","guid":"Bh-jLIUIK0rPDex3AFPaNw","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"252","text":"• Deficiencias en MAC (C5-C9) → Infecciones recurrentes por Neisseria.","guid":"XYiFtMy1BtsJJXTW3xX1JQ","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":255,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"FP Inmunología básica-2024-1","id":"map_752","resolved_references":[]}